title: Pregame squabble: Tuskegee vs Stillman
text: Pregame squabble: Tuskegee vs Stillman Buy Photo A brief pregame incident sent coaching staff from both teams and other officials scrambling to get between Tuskegee and Stillman players on Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in Tuskegee. The incident was quickly calmed and both teams went on to play.
